>\n<br />\n成日同自己講上連登勿認真，可能我今次真係認真左。<br />\n<br />\n係其他Po見到，覺得篇文寫得好好😭"},{"pid":"9d5bb0b6fdff0a5f0b084d9e3585f03e0853ad65","tid":432294,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班死廢青正係識比負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e1f190742b1d47f4abf17eb44b044e734a5bd4f4","tid":432294,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"睇落點都好過689"},{"pid":"005eb86149e65cc430a2ec67d8f07fac2c9c036b","tid":432294,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇落點都好過689</blockquote><br />\n689應該港毒啲鬼黎"},{"pid":"fd8bc5646d6874f7d2a2c56437c25cfb4dafc694","tid":432294,"uid":56432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得佢係新嘅戴卓爾夫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n你應該撳錯emoji，已經幫你改返，唔使唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔好歪曲我意思啦，你想歌頌呢個婆娘未免大早啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkg